create or replace PROCEDURE         "BRF38A_MAPPING_PROCEDURE" (REPORT_DATE VARCHAR2)
 
IS
 
  V_REPORT_DATE DATE := To_date (REPORT_DATE, 'DD-MM-YYYY');

   V_FROM_DATE dATE :=  ADD_MONTHS (LAST_DAY (REPORT_DATE), -1) + 1;

BEGIN
--DEVELOPED BY - SURIYA
--OUTWARD
INSERT INTO BRF38A_MAPPING_TABLE
(CUST_ID,FORACID,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,COUNTRY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,REPORT_DATE)
SELECT CUST_ID,ACCT_NO,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,REM_CNTRY,COLLECTION_AMT,REPORT_DATE FROM brf_rem_table 
where collection_code in ('OUTTTTORTT','OUTTTTIMTT') AND REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE;


--INWARD
INSERT INTO BRF38A_MAPPING_TABLE
(CUST_ID,FORACID,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,COUNTRY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,REPORT_DATE)
SELECT CUST_ID,ACCT_NO,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,REM_CNTRY,COLLECTION_AMT,REPORT_DATE FROM brf_rem_table 
where collection_code in ('INWTTTIRTT','INWTTTIREX') AND REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE;
COMMIT;
END;

--MAPPING PROCEDURE B

create or replace PROCEDURE         "BRF38B_MAPPING_PROCEDURE" (REPORT_DATE VARCHAR2)
 
IS
 
  V_REPORT_DATE DATE := To_date (REPORT_DATE, 'DD-MM-YYYY')  ;

   V_FROM_DATE dATE :=  ADD_MONTHS (LAST_DAY (REPORT_DATE), -1) + 1 ;

BEGIN
--DEVELOPED BY - SURIYA
---DATE -- 1/13/2024

/*INSERT INTO BRF38A_MAPPING_TABLE
(CUST_ID,FORACID,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,COUNTRY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,REPORT_DATE)
SELECT CUST_ID,ACCT_NO,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,REM_CNTRY,COLLECTION_AMT,REPORT_DATE FROM brf_rem_table 
where collection_code in ('OUTTTTORTT','OUTTTTIMTT') AND REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE  ;


--INWARD
INSERT INTO BRF38A_MAPPING_TABLE
(CUST_ID,FORACID,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,COUNTRY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,REPORT_DATE)
SELECT CUST_ID,ACCT_NO,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,REM_CNTRY,COLLECTION_AMT,REPORT_DATE FROM brf_rem_table 
where collection_code in ('INWTTTIRTT','INWTTTIREX') AND REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE ;*/
/*MERGE INTO BRF38B_MAPPING_TABLE b
USING (
    SELECT 
        CUST_ID, 
        MAX(FORACID) AS FORACID,
        COUNTRY,
        PURPOSE_OF_REM,
        COLLECTION_CODE
    FROM 
        BRF38A_MAPPING_TABLE
    GROUP BY 
        CUST_ID, COUNTRY, PURPOSE_OF_REM, COLLECTION_CODE
) a ON (b.CUST_ID = a.CUST_ID AND b.REPORT_DATE = TO_DATE('30-JUN-2023', 'DD-MON-YYYY') and b.COUNTRY = a.COUNTRY )
WHEN MATCHED THEN
    UPDATE SET 
        b.FORACID = a.FORACID,
        b.PURPOSE_OF_REM = a.PURPOSE_OF_REM,
        b.COLLECTION_CODE = a.COLLECTION_CODE
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
    INSERT (CUST_ID, FORACID, REPORT_DATE, COUNTRY,
        PURPOSE_OF_REM,
        COLLECTION_CODE)
    VALUES (a.CUST_ID, a.FORACID, TO_DATE('30-JUN-2023'), a.COUNTRY,
        a.PURPOSE_OF_REM,
        a.COLLECTION_CODE)  ;

COMMIT ;*/

--MERGE INTO BRF38B_MAPPING_TABLE b
--USING (
--    SELECT 
--        CUST_ID, 
--        MAX(FORACID) AS FORACID,
--        COUNTRY,
--        PURPOSE_OF_REM,

--) a ON (b.CUST_ID = a.CUST_ID and b.foracid = a.foracid AND b.REPORT_DATE = TO_DATE('30-JUN-2023', 'DD-MON-YYYY') and b.COUNTRY = a.COUNTRY )
--WHEN MATCHED THEN
--    UPDATE SET 
--        b.FORACID = a.FORACID,

--        b.COLLECTION_CODE = a.COLLECTION_CODE,
--        b.country = a.country  ;
--        
--insert

INSERT INTO BRF38B_MAPPING_TABLE
(CUST_ID,FORACID,COUNTRY,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,REPORT_DATE)
SELECT CUST_ID, FORACID,COUNTRY,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE, SUM(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC) AS sum_of_unique_values,REPORT_DATE
FROM BRF38A_MAPPING_TABLE where REPORT_DATE =V_REPORT_DATE
GROUP BY CUST_ID,FORACID,COUNTRY, PURPOSE_OF_REM, COLLECTION_CODE,REPORT_DATE
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT FORACID) = 1  ;

--ROW102A  --OUTWARD FAMILY   
UPDATE  BRF38B_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF38',REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102',report_addl_criteria_1 = 'North American Countries',
report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Canada' ,report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW102A' 
WHERE  collection_code in ('OUTTTTORTT','OUTTTTIMTT') AND COUNTRY IN ('CA') AND PURPOSE_OF_REM IN ('EDU','EDUCA','FAM') AND REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE ; 
COMMIT ;

--ROW102B     --OUTWARD INVESTMENT
UPDATE  BRF38B_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF38',REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102',report_addl_criteria_1 = 'North American Countries',
report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Canada',report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW102B' 
WHERE   collection_code in ('OUTTTTORTT','OUTTTTIMTT') AND COUNTRY IN ('CA') AND PURPOSE_OF_REM IN ('CEA','CIN','FIA','PIN') AND REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE ;
COMMIT ;

--ROW102C     ---OUTWARD TRADE
UPDATE  BRF38B_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF38',REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102',report_addl_criteria_1 = 'North American Countries',
report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Canada',report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW102C' 
WHERE  collection_code in ('OUTTTTORTT','OUTTTTIMTT') AND COUNTRY IN ('CA') AND PURPOSE_OF_REM IN ('FDL','GDE','GDI','LEL',
'P1301','TCP','TCR') AND REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE ;
COMMIT ;

--ROW102D     ---OUTWARD OTHER
UPDATE  BRF38B_MAPPING_TABLE SET  REPORT_NAME_1 ='BRF38',REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102',report_addl_criteria_1 = 'North American Countries',
report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Canada',report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW102D' 
WHERE  collection_code in ('OUTTTTORTT','OUTTTTIMTT') AND COUNTRY IN ('CA') AND  PURPOSE_OF_REM NOT IN ('EDU','EDUCA','FAM','CEA','CIN','FIA'
,'PIN','FDL','GDE','GDI','LEL','P1301','TCP','TCR') AND REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE ; 
COMMIT ;

--DETAIL A PROCEDURE

create or replace PROCEDURE         "BRF38A_DETAIL_PROCEDURE" (REPORT_DATE DATE)
IS
  V_REPORT_DATE DATE := To_date (REPORT_DATE, 'DD-MM-YYYY'); 

BEGIN


delete from BRF38A_DETAILTABLE where REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE;
Commit;


--OUTWARD + INWARD
INSERT INTO BRF38A_DETAILTABLE
(CUST_ID,FORACID,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,COUNTRY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,REPORT_DATE,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_NAME_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3)
SELECT CUST_ID,FORACID,PURPOSE_OF_REM,COLLECTION_CODE,COUNTRY,ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC,REPORT_DATE,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_NAME_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3 FROM BRF38B_MAPPING_TABLE 
where  REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE AND REPORT_LABEL_1 IS NOT NULL ;

COMMIT;
END;

--DEVLOPED BY -SURIYA K
--DATE - 1/13/2024
--DETAIL B PROCEDURE

create or replace PROCEDURE         "BRF38B_DETAIL_PROCEDURE" (REPORT_DATE VARCHAR2)
IS
  V_REPORT_DATE DATE := To_date (REPORT_DATE, 'DD-MM-YYYY'); 

BEGIN



delete from BRF38B_DETAILTABLE where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE;
Commit;


MERGE INTO BRF38B_DETAILTABLE b
USING (
    SELECT 
      DISTINCT  COUNTRY,
        MAX(CUST_ID) AS CUST_ID,
        MAX(REPORT_LABEL_1) AS REPORT_LABEL_1,
        MAX(REPORT_NAME_1) AS REPORT_NAME_1,
        MAX(REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1) AS REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
        MAX(REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2) AS REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,
        MAX(REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3) AS REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,
        SUM(TotalBalance) AS TotalBalance
    FROM (
        SELECT 
            CUST_ID, 
            COUNTRY,
            REPORT_LABEL_1,
            REPORT_NAME_1,
            REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
            REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,
            REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,
            FORACID,
            (SELECT SUM(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC) FROM BRF38A_DETAILTABLE WHERE CUST_ID = a.CUST_ID) AS TotalBalance
        FROM 
            BRF38A_DETAILTABLE a
    ) aggregated_data
    GROUP BY COUNTRY
) a ON (b.COUNTRY = a.COUNTRY AND b.REPORT_DATE = V_REPORT_DATE)
WHEN MATCHED THEN
    UPDATE SET 
        b.CUST_ID = a.CUST_ID,
        b.ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC = a.TotalBalance,
        b.REPORT_LABEL_1 = a.REPORT_LABEL_1,
        b.REPORT_NAME_1 = a.REPORT_NAME_1,
        b.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1 = a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,
        b.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2 = a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,
        b.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3 = a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
    INSERT (CUST_ID, ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC, REPORT_DATE, REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,
    REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,REPORT_LABEL_1,REPORT_NAME_1)
    VALUES (a.CUST_ID,a.TotalBalance, V_REPORT_DATE,a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2,a.REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3,
    a.REPORT_LABEL_1,a.REPORT_NAME_1);

COMMIT;
--ROW179
UPDATE BRF38B_DETAILTABLE
SET FAMILY_OUTWARD = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF38A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW179A' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Afghanistan'
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW179' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Afghanistan'  AND REPORT_DATE =V_REPORT_DATE ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF38B_DETAILTABLE
SET INVESTMENT_OUTWARD = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF38A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW179B' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Afghanistan'
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW179' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Afghanistan'  AND REPORT_DATE =V_REPORT_DATE ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF38B_DETAILTABLE
SET TRADE_OUTWARD = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF38A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW179C' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Afghanistan'
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW179' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Afghanistan'  AND REPORT_DATE =V_REPORT_DATE ;
COMMIT;

SET OTHER_OUTWARD = (

WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW270' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Zimbabwe'  AND REPORT_DATE =V_REPORT_DATE ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF38B_DETAILTABLE
SET TRADE_INWARD = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF38A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW270G' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Zimbabwe'
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW270' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Zimbabwe'  AND REPORT_DATE =V_REPORT_DATE ;
COMMIT;

UPDATE BRF38B_DETAILTABLE
SET OTHER_INWARD = (
    SELECT round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0))
    FROM BRF38A_DETAILTABLE
    WHERE report_addl_criteria_3 = 'ROW270H' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Zimbabwe'
)
WHERE REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW270' AND report_addl_criteria_2 = 'Zimbabwe'  AND REPORT_DATE =V_REPORT_DATE ;
COMMIT;



commit;
end;
--SUMMARY PROCEUDRE

BEGIN 

delete from BRF38A_SUMMARYTABLE  where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE;
Commit;

DELETE FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE B WHERE report_date = V_REPORT_DATE;
Commit;
--REMAINING_COUNTRIES
INSERT INTO BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE (ROW_LABEL,COUNTRY_BREAK_DOWN,
REMAINING_COUNTRIES,REPORT_DATE,OUTWARD_FAMILY1, OUTWARD_INVESTMENT1, OUTWARD_TRADE1, OUTWARD_OTHER1,
 INWARD_FAMILY1, INWARD_INVESTMENT1, INWARD_TRADE1, INWARD_OTHER1)
SELECT  REPORT_LABEL_1, REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1,REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_2 ,
REPORT_DATE ,FAMILY_OUTWARD, INVESTMENT_OUTWARD, TRADE_OUTWARD, OTHER_OUTWARD,
FAMILY_INWARD, INVESTMENT_INWARD, TRADE_INWARD, OTHER_INWARD FROM BRF38B_DETAILTABLE
where report_date = '30-JUN-2023'
and REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_1 IN 'Remaining Countries' ;

select round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0)) into V_R11_OUTWARD_FAMILY from BRF38A_DETAILTABLE where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE AND  REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102' AND REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3= 'ROW102A';
select round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0)) into V_R11_OUTWARD_INVESTMENT from BRF38A_DETAILTABLE where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE AND  REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102' AND REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3= 'ROW102B';
select round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0)) into V_R11_OUTWARD_TRADE from BRF38A_DETAILTABLE where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE AND  REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102' AND REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3= 'ROW102C';
select round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0)) into V_R11_OUTWARD_OTHER from BRF38A_DETAILTABLE where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE AND  REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102' AND REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3= 'ROW102D';
V_R11_OUTWARD_TOTAL:=V_R11_OUTWARD_FAMILY+V_R11_OUTWARD_INVESTMENT+V_R11_OUTWARD_TRADE+V_R11_OUTWARD_OTHER ;
select round(nvl(sum(abs(ACT_BALANCE_AMT_LC))/1000,0)) into V_R11_INWARD_FAMILY from BRF38A_DETAILTABLE where report_date = V_REPORT_DATE AND  REPORT_LABEL_1 = 'ROW102' AND REPORT_ADDL_CRITERIA_3= 'ROW102E';

V_R10_OUTWARD_FAMILY:= V_R11_OUTWARD_FAMILY+V_R12_OUTWARD_FAMILY;

V_R10_OUTWARD_OTHER:= V_R11_OUTWARD_OTHER+V_R12_OUTWARD_OTHER;
--OUTWARD TOTAL
V_R10_OUTWARD_TOTAL:=V_R10_OUTWARD_FAMILY+V_R10_OUTWARD_INVESTMENT+V_R10_OUTWARD_TRADE+V_R10_OUTWARD_OTHER;
--INWARD TOTAL
V_R10_INWARD_FAMILY:= V_R11_INWARD_FAMILY+V_R12_INWARD_FAMILY;

----REMANING TOTAL
update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set OUTWARD_FAMILY_REM =(SELECT SUM(OUTWARD_FAMILY1) 
FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE);
update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set outward_investment_rem =(SELECT SUM(OUTWARD_INVESTMENT1) 
FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE);
update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set OUTWARD_TRADE_rem = (SELECT  SUM(OUTWARD_TRADE1)
FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE);
update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set OUTWARD_OTHER_rem = (SELECT SUM(OUTWARD_OTHER1)
FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE);

update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set OUTWARD_TOTAL_REM = OUTWARD_OTHER_rem +OUTWARD_TRADE_rem +
OUTWARD_FAMILY_REM +outward_investment_rem;

update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set INWARD_FAMILY_REM =(SELECT SUM(INWARD_FAMILY1) 
FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE);
update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set INWARD_investment_rem =(SELECT SUM(INWARD_INVESTMENT1) 
FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE);
update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set INWARD_TRADE_rem = (SELECT  SUM(INWARD_TRADE1)
FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE);
update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set INWARD_OTHER_rem = (SELECT SUM(INWARD_OTHER1)
FROM BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE);

update BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE set INWARD_TOTAL_REM = INWARD_OTHER_rem +INWARD_TRADE_rem +
INWARD_FAMILY_REM +INWARD_investment_rem;


 SELECT max(OUTWARD_FAMILY_REM) into V_OUTWARD_FAMILY_REM  FROM 
 BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE;
 SELECT max(OUTWARD_INVESTMENT_REM) into v_outward_investment_rem  FROM 
 BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE;
 SELECT max(OUTWARD_TRADE_REM) into V_outward_trade_rem  FROM 
 BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE;
 SELECT max(OUTWARD_OTHER_REM) into V_outward_other_rem  FROM 
 BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE;

 SELECT max(INWARD_FAMILY_REM) into V_INWARD_FAMILY_REM  FROM 
 BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE;
 SELECT max(INWARD_INVESTMENT_REM) into v_inward_investment_rem  FROM 
 BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE;
 SELECT max(INWARD_TRADE_REM) into V_inward_trade_rem  FROM 
 BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE;
 SELECT max(INWARD_OTHER_REM) into V_inward_other_rem  FROM 
 BRF38B_SUMMARYTABLE;

--GRAND TOTAL
  V_OUTWARD_FAMILY := V_OUTWARD_FAMILY+ V_OUTWARD_FAMILY_REM;
  V_OUTWARD_INVESTMENT:= V_OUTWARD_INVESTMENT+ v_outward_investment_rem;
  V_OUTWARD_TRADE:= V_OUTWARD_TRADE +  V_outward_trade_rem;
 V_OUTWARD_OTHER:= V_OUTWARD_OTHER + V_outward_other_rem;
  V_INWARD_FAMILY := V_INWARD_FAMILY+ V_inward_family_rem;
  V_INWARD_INVESTMENT:= V_INWARD_INVESTMENT+ V_inward_investment_rem;
  V_INWARD_TRADE:= V_INWARD_TRADE +  V_inward_trade_rem;
 V_INWARD_OTHER:= V_INWARD_OTHER + V_inward_other_rem;
--GRAND TOTAL SIDE
V_OUTWARD_TOTAL:=V_OUTWARD_FAMILY+V_OUTWARD_INVESTMENT+V_OUTWARD_TRADE+V_OUTWARD_OTHER;
V_INWARD_TOTAL:=V_INWARD_FAMILY+V_INWARD_INVESTMENT+V_INWARD_TRADE+V_INWARD_OTHER;
